\c 14
\s Ukubusa kukaAmaziya
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wesibili kaJowashi indodana kaJehowazi, inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 13.10.\x*, uAmaziya indodana kaJowashi inkosi yakoJuda waba yinkosi\x + 12.21. 2 Lan. 25.1-4.\x*.
\v 2 Wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lanhlanu lapho esiba yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amabili lesificamunwemunye eJerusalema. Lebizo likanina lalinguJehowadani weJerusalema.
\v 3 Wasesenza okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, kodwa kungenjengoDavida uyise; wenza njengakho konke uJowashi uyise akwenzayo.
\v 4 Loba kunjalo indawo eziphakemeyo kazisuswanga; abantu babelokhu benikela imihlatshelo betshisa impepha endaweni eziphakemeyo\x + 12.3. 15.4,35. 16.4. 1 Kho. 15.14.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Kwasekusithi umbuso wakhe usuqinisiwe esandleni sakhe, watshaya inceku zakhe ezazitshaye inkosi uyise\x + 12.20.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa abantwana bababulali kababulalanga, njengokubhaliweyo ogwalweni lomlayo kaMozisi lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalaya khona isithi: Oyise kabayikubulawa ngenxa yabantwana, labantwana kabayikubulawa ngenxa yaboyise, kodwa wonke umuntu uzabulawelwa isono sakhe\x + Dute. 24.16. Jer. 31.30. Hez. 18.4,20.\x*.
\v 7 Yena wasetshaya amaEdoma\x + 2 Lan. 25.11.\x* azinkulungwane ezilitshumi esihotsheni setshwayi, wathumba iSela ngempi\x + 2 Sam. 8.13. 1 Lan. 18.12. Hlab. 60.\x*, wabiza ibizo layo ngokuthi yiJokhitheyeli, kuze kube lamuhla\x + Josh. 15.38.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Khona uAmaziya wathuma izithunywa kuJehowashi indodana kaJehowahazi indodana kaJehu, inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 2 Lan. 25.17-24.\x*, esithi: Woza sikhangelane ubuso ngobuso\x + 14.11. 23.29. 2 Lan. 25.13.\x*.
\v 9 UJehowashi inkosi yakoIsrayeli wasethumela kuAmaziya inkosi yakoJuda esithi: Ukhula oluhlabayo oluseLebhanoni\x + Hlu. 9.8.\x* lwathumela emsedarini oseLebhanoni\x + Hlu. 9.15.\x* lusithi: Nika indodakazi yakho endodaneni yami ibe ngumka\add yo\add*; kwasekusedlula isilo seganga esiseLebhanoni, salugxoba ukhula oluhlabayo.
\v 10 Uyitshayile lokuyitshaya iEdoma, inhliziyo yakho isikuphakamisile\x + Dute. 8.14. 2 Lan. 26.16. 32.25. Hez. 28.2,5,17.\x*; dumiseka, uhlale endlini yakho; ngoba kungani uzivusela ububi ukuze uwe wena loJuda kanye lawe\x + Dute. 2.5.\x*?
\v 11 Kodwa uAmaziya kezwanga. Ngakho uJehowashi inkosi yakoIsrayeli wenyuka, yena-ke loAmaziya inkosi yakoJuda bakhangelana ubuso ngobuso eBeti-Shemeshi eyakoJuda\x + Josh. 15.10.\x*.
\v 12 UJuda wasetshaywa phambi kukaIsrayeli; basebebaleka, ngulowo lalowo waya ethenteni lakhe\x + 1 Sam. 4.10. 2 Sam. 18.17.\x*.
\v 13 UJehowashi inkosi yakoIsrayeli wasembamba uAmaziya inkosi yakoJuda, indodana kaJehowashi indodana kaAhaziya, eBeti-Shemeshi\x + Josh. 15.10.\x*; wafika eJerusalema, wadilizela phansi umduli weJerusalema, kusukela esangweni lakoEfrayimi\x + Neh. 8.16.\x* kusiya esangweni lengonsi, ingalo ezingamakhulu amane\x + 2 Lan. 26.9. Jer. 31.38. Zek. 14.10. 2 Lan. 25.23.\x*.
\v 14 Wasethatha lonke igolide lesiliva, lezitsha zonke ezatholakala endlini kaJehova lezendlini zenotho zendlu yenkosi, kanye labayisibambiso, wasebuyela eSamariya\x + 12.18. 1 Kho. 7.51.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJehowashi azenzayo, lamandla akhe, lokuthi walwa njani loAmaziya inkosi yakoJuda, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli\x + 13.12,13.\x*?
\v 16 UJehowashi waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa eSamariya emakhosini akoIsrayeli. UJerobhowamu indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\p
\v 17 UAmaziya indodana kaJowashi, inkosi yakoJuda, wasephila iminyaka elitshumi lanhlanu emva kokufa kukaJehowashi indodana kaJehowahazi inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 2 Lan. 25.25. 26.2.\x*.
\v 18 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaAmaziya, kazibhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda?
\v 19 Basebemenzela ugobe eJerusalema\x + 2 Lan. 25.27.\x*, wabalekela eLakishi; kodwa bathuma bamlandela eLakishi, bambulalela khona\x + Josh. 10.3.\x*.
\v 20 Basebemthwala ngamabhiza, wangcwatshelwa eJerusalema kuboyise emzini kaDavida.
\p
\v 21 Bonke abantu bakoJuda basebethatha uAzariya, owayeleminyaka elitshumi lesithupha, bambeka waba yinkosi esikhundleni sikayise uAmaziya.
\v 22 Yena wakha iElathi\x + 16.6. Dute. 2 Kho. 26. 2 Lan. 8.17. 26.2.\x*, wayibuyisela koJuda emva kokulala kwenkosi laboyise.
\s Ukubusa kukaJerobhowamu
\p
\v 23 Ngomnyaka wetshumi lanhlanu kaAmaziya indodana kaJowashi inkosi yakoJuda uJerobhowamu indodana kaJowashi inkosi yakoIsrayeli waba yinkosi eSamariya; \add wabusa\add* iminyaka engamatshumi amane lanye.
\v 24 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*; kasukanga ezonweni zonke zikaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati owenza uIsrayeli one\x + 1 Kho. 14.16.\x*.
\v 25 Yena wabuyisela umngcele wakoIsrayeli kusukela ekungeneni kweHamathi\x + 1 Kho. 8.65.\x* kuze kufike elwandle lwamagceke, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + Dute. 3.17. 4.49. Josh. 3.16.\x*, eyalikhuluma ngesandla senceku yayo uJona indodana kaAmithayi umprofethi\x + Jona 1.1. Mat. 12.39,40.\x*, owayevela eGathi-Heferi\x + Josh. 19.13.\x*.
\v 26 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yabona ukuhlupheka kukaIsrayeli, kwakubaba kakhulu\x + 13.4. Eks. 3.7.\x*, ngoba kwakungekho ovalelweyo, njalo engekho okhululekileyo, njalo kungelamsizi kaIsrayeli\x + Dute. 32.36.\x*.
\v 27 IN\nd kosi\nd* yayingatshongo-ke ukuthi izalesula ibizo likaIsrayeli ngaphansi kwamazulu; kodwa yabasindisa ngesandla sikaJerobhowamu indodana kaJowashi\x + 13.5,23.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJerobhowamu, lakho konke akwenzayo, lamandla akhe, ukuthi walwa njani, lokuthi wayibuyisela njani koIsrayeli iDamaseko leHamathi\x + 1 Kho. 11.24.\x*, engeyeJuda\x + 2 Sam. 8.6. 1 Kho. 11.24. 1 Lan. 18.5,6. 2 Lan. 8.3.\x*, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli?
\v 29 UJerobhowamu waselala laboyise, emakhosini akoIsrayeli. UZekhariya indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.